overview: The “Home” longboard surfing video is a journey down Australia’s East Coast, dropping in on and hanging out with some of Australia’s best longboarders. Finding out about their place, their mates, their waves, their home.  Surfers: Beau Young, Bonga Perkins, Harley Ingleby, Josh Constable, Dave Simons, Grant Thomas, Dane Wilson, Dane Pioli, Julian Wilson, Jai Lee, Matt Kay Harrison Roach, Andrew Logreco, Isaac Paddon and many more.
title: Home
